data.description: Welcome home to this charming mid-century ranch nestled on a private cul-de-sac in Pine Hills. This well-maintained home features one level-living with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and sunny den with fireplace. The updated eat-in kitchen features clean white cabinets and stainless appliances. Outside, enjoy the privacy of the brick patio and the relaxing sound of the water feature and koi pond. A large 2-car garage and additional parking pad out front offers ample space for your cars, and easy turnaround for your guests. At the end of the block is Shady Valley Park with a playground, tennis courts and soccer field. With easy access to GA 400, I-85, Emory, the CDC, Lenox Mall, Phipps Plaza, Midtown and Buckhead, the location can't be beat. Homes like this are few and far between, so don't miss out on this one!
